---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Contact
description: "Get in touch with Manuela to book a free consultation or ask about Portuguese tutoring classes in Vancouver, BC."
---

{% block content %}

<!-- Page Hero -->
<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Get in Touch</h1>
    <p>I&rsquo;d love to hear from you. Whether you have a question or you&rsquo;re ready to get started, my inbox is always open.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Contact section -->
<section class="section">
  <div class="container contact-email">
    <h2 style="color: var(--color-secondary);">Say Olá!</h2>
    <p style="max-width: 540px; margin-inline: auto; color: var(--color-text-muted);">
      The easiest way to reach me is by email. Tell me a little about yourself — your current level, your goals, and what excites you about learning Portuguese.
    </p>

    <div style="margin: 2.5rem 0;">
      <!-- TODO: Replace the placeholder email below with Manuela's real email address -->
      <a href="mailto:manuela@example.com" class="btn btn--primary" style="font-size: 1.1rem; padding: 0.85em 2em;">
        ✉️ &nbsp; manuela@example.com
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="contact-response">
      <span>⏱️</span>
      <span>I typically reply within 24 hours, Monday to Friday.</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- What to expect -->
<section class="section section--alt">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section__header">
      <h2>What Happens Next?</h2>
      <p>No pressure, no commitment — just a friendly conversation about your goals.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid-3">
      <div class="card text-center">
        <div class="card__icon" style="text-align: center;">1️⃣</div>
        <h3>You Reach Out</h3>
        <p>Send me an email with a little about yourself and what you&rsquo;re hoping to achieve with Portuguese.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card text-center">
        <div class="card__icon" style="text-align: center;">2️⃣</div>
        <h3>Free Consultation</h3>
        <p>We&rsquo;ll schedule a free 20-minute call to assess your current level and discuss which class suits you best.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card text-center">
        <div class="card__icon" style="text-align: center;">3️⃣</div>
        <h3>Start Learning!</h3>
        <p>We set a schedule, get you signed up, and your Portuguese journey begins. Bem-vindo!</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- CTA Banner -->
<section class="cta-banner">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Ready? Let&rsquo;s Begin.</h2>
    <p>Your first lesson is closer than you think. Reach out today.</p>
    <!-- TODO: Replace the placeholder email below with Manuela's real email address -->
    <a href="mailto:manuela@example.com" class="btn btn--white">Send an Email</a>
  </div>
</section>

{% endblock %}
